site_name: Land At 27 To 37 Lascars Avenue And 14 To 23
description: Application for the change of use of existing buildings, to provide 457 student bed spaces with ancillary facilities together with retail floor space (Use Classes E and F.1) at ground floor, alongside the construction of a canopy structure to link the two building blocks together with the provision of ancillary refuse/cycle stores, servicing areas, blue badge car parking, landscaping and other associated works.
